reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice looking and sturdy lamp set. Color: Rustic.
reviews.reviewText: Great Lamp set. The 'rustic' color option is more grey than I expected but overall these lamps are sturdy, go together easily and look nice. The lamps arrived packaged very well. I appreciate the functions of the night light options and two usb charging ports built into each base. I also like that the light switches are on the base as well so I don't have fumble around feeling for the light switch under the shade. These lamps add to the 'creature comfort' of our living space.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Package arrived on time, with no damage externally or internally. Instructions were minimal, but understandable. Once assembled, the shades sit and stay level, with no wrinkles or gaps. The Lu men’s are perfect for what we wanted, and needed. Love the color of the base and shade. The two switches make it convenient to have the amount of light you require. The two USB plugs make it convenient to plug in gadgets. If I had one suggestion for the manufacture, it would be to make one of them usb c, since it seems most phones are headed that way. Overall, we are extremely happy with these lamps. The quality, fit, and finish are all on point.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This turned out to be a nice light set for the money. They look like good quality lights. They light well and do a nice job. The light in the bottom acts as a good night light. They need to be assembled and the cord was difficult to get into the light. The lamp shade is easier to put together with two people. They looks good.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Well worth the price! Easy to assemble and don’t be put off by the Velcro shades. Looks amazing. These are very well made lamps as I was afraid they would be top heavy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Yep! Great choice. Look good and love the two different ways to use the lights. To brighten up my room or as a nightlight. Wish I had bought them sooner. Personally, I didn’t like the shades that came with them and put different ones on. Actually used the lampshades from them lamps I replaced. So these lamps are very sturdy but the shades were not as sturdy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewText: These are great lamps. I like that the switch are on the bottom of the lamp. The usb charging plugs is a plus too.

reviews.reviewText: These lamps are beautiful! They are perfect for our bedroom nightstands! They are the perfect size...not too big and not too small. We absolutely love the smokey glass base, too! I highly recommend these lamps.
